{"tid":1233221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文慎入]今朝見到有巴打話畀個呀婆定唔知呀嬸搶嘢","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:14:02.000Z","uid":1035,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94b0cfed5274951ddc0e0217a170232915fc6e7d","tid":1233221,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"我想講我今日去食麵都畀個呀叔打！<br />\n事緣我約咗我女朋友同佢屋企人一齊去遊行<br />\n咁就約好各自食埋晏先出嚟<br />\n咁我冇乜idea就決定去我食開嗰間麵檔隊返個腩米同埋腐乳生菜先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到差唔多埋尾 醒起今日要行好耐喎應該燒到好多卡路里<br />\n咁又叫多咗支大可樂當獎勵下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就喺支可樂放上我枱冇耐 突然冇個呀叔行埋嚟<br />\n叔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：年輕人 你今日係咪都去遊行呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：(即刻嚇到跳曬掣) 係⋯係呀⋯⋯<br />\n我一講完 佢就立刻使出佢苦練多年嘅降龍十八掌 大大力咁拍咗我膊頭幾下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你快啲去啦 你張單等我埋就得架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：吓 唔使喎⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：得架啦 年輕人 放心啦 我撐你 呢餐飯就當我請你啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔⋯唔使啦⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：得架啦 走啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁 咁多謝曬先⋯⋯<br />\n喺嗰時我真係完全唔識畀反應 即刻急急腳啜曬成支可樂就走人<br />\n最尷尬嘅係 同我同枱好似都有個人係準備去遊行嘅 但個呀叔好似睇佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過咗一整日遊行 返到屋企再慢慢沉澱返成件事<br />\n發覺我哋香港呢個地方真係有好多好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係我哋嗰份香港心喺呢幾年慢慢畀唔同嘅事情搞到麻目咗 大家都開始收收埋埋<br />\n所以香港人 經過咗今次呢件事 大家記得多啲拎你哋嘅香港心出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人好事要寫得詳細啲 如有1999請見諒"},{"pid":"31aa94fd88daa5095c8d4f9c94da361291d05803","tid":1233221,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"btw喺呢度我想同嗰位叔叔講多次多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信大家都係住埋同一區嘅街坊 下次見到你一定一定要畀我請返你食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84e28c2174a73d36644a36c91fe0723710d8ccd","tid":1233221,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"好人好事要推畀更多人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da694ee074137e6e1219855d568eddc7c71dee7","tid":1233221,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"好人好事係好<br />\n<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 我地未爭取到任何野架</span>"},{"pid":"28b1b1b79ee83f6a5f1954ad02a11f953d0a4bc7","tid":1233221,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da694ee074137e6e1219855d568eddc7c71dee7","tid":1233221,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"好人好事係好<br />\n<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 我地未爭取到任何野架</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:09:32.000Z","msg":"同意！！！！！！！<br />\n但係都唔代表我哋唔需要花時間去表揚喺呢一日發生過嘅好人好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d2e57b9ce65555558f594e76f4f69d6b0fe28b","tid":1233221,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:14:02.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}